Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' before transitioning to 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Total duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + In Progress and the end of the case

Name: Average duration from 'Accepted + In Progress' to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Longest duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' before any transition
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Accepted + In Progress' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x000001E27CECF0A0> - AppliesTo.PROCESS

Name: Shortest duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' before transitioning to 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' in cases where 'Accepted + Wait - User' follows
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Total duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' before 'Accepted + Assigned'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Accepted + Assigned'

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' in cases that involve 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'

Name: Total duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' in cases ending with 'Completed + Cancelled'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Average duration between 'Accepted + In Progress' and 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'

Name: Duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' in the fastest case to reach 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' in the slowest case to reach 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The maximum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' in cases that do not transition directly to 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + In Progress and the end of the case

Name: Total cumulative duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' for all cases in the log
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + In Progress and the end of the case

Name: Duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' in cases that transition to 'Completed + In Call' within the shortest time frame
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Median duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' in cases leading to 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Duration variance of 'Accepted + In Progress' across different countries
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and the end of case grouped by the last value of resource country

Name: Median duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' in cases with more than one occurrence of this activity
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' before transitioning to any 'Completed' status
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Longest and shortest duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' across all variants
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Accepted + In Progress' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x000001E27CECF0A0> - AppliesTo.PROCESS
